cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

The paper presents a decentralized algorithm for mobile sensors to gather and assimilate data for predicting traffic phenomena, which involves machine learning and control theory. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with networked systems and communication, which suggests cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper uses Gaussian process models and active sensing, which are topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
